description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: Fauci and the NIH suppressed evidence of the Wuhan lab leak theory. Paul vs. Fauci on the origins of covid, role of gain of function research funding from U.S. Medical experts throughout history have often been wrong. Paul suggests criminal charges for Fauci. C&B recommend book: The Ghost Map. CNN's Don Lemon calls Rand Paul an idiot.
